This has a lot of wonderful flavors. I made the following changes: I used olive salad, instead of just green olives, boneless skinless chicken thighs instead of breast halves, black pepper instead of salt and added 1/2 cup of chicken stock to the sauce as it was sauteing. Served with shell pasta and green beans.

