This dish is amazing!! 4+++++++ stars!! If you like green olives then you will LOVE this recipe! It's so simple to make and incredibly tasteful. I added extra olives and lemon peel. You can't go wrong! The cumin/red pepper makes it spicy and so delicious. I highly recommend this. If you make for guest, just make sure they like green olives (a lot of people don't).

